    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>Wait, I'm a bit confused. You just said it has a \"positive impact\" but then you immediately called it a \"work disincentive\" which sounds like a negative thing? Which one is it actually? Is the safety net actually making people want to work less?",
